N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4602.6 - Reinstatement of license

State Regulations

When a license has been suspended or revoked and the
suspension or revocation is set aside and the license reinstated, the original
license shall not be reissued. In such case the applicant shall file a new
application and a new license shall be issued. Notes
